<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AbbyBunnyCat 的測驗遊戲大廳 🐾</title>
    <style>
        /* 基礎樣式設定 */
        body {
            font-family: 'PingFang TC', 'Microsoft JhengHei', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d1117; /* 搭配 GitHub 的深色主題，質感很好 */
            color: #c9d1d9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #58a6ff;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* 6 個卡片的網格排版 */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* 卡片設計 */
        .card {
            background-color: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #c9d1d9;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* 滑鼠懸停效果 */
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            border-color: #58a6ff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #f0f6fc;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #8b949e;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>AbbyBunnyCat 的小測驗大廳 🔮</h1>
        <p>點擊下方卡片，開啟你的探索旅程吧！</p>
    </header>

    <main class="grid-container">

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/boundary/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">🚧</div>
            <h2>Boundary</h2>
            <p>點擊進入測驗，探索你的專屬邊界。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/mbti100/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
            <h2>MBTI 100</h2>
            <p>100% 深入的性格分析小測驗。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/cosmic_oracle/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">🌌</div>
            <h2>Cosmic Oracle</h2>
            <p>宇宙神諭，為你當下的迷惘解惑。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/office_fortune/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">💼</div>
            <h2>Office Fortune</h2>
            <p>職場運勢大補帖，看看今天工作順不順！</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/cosmic-fortune/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">✨</div>
            <h2>Cosmic Fortune</h2>
            <p>連結星空的力量，測出你的今日好運。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://abbybunnycat.github.io/kuanyin/" target="_blank" class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">🙏</div>
            <h2>觀音靈籤</h2>
            <p>虔誠祈願，求取你的指引籤詩。</p>
        </a>

    </main>

</body>
</html>
